title: 6 FT Mini Plug 3.5mm 1/8" Audio Extension Cable
description: 6' Mini Plug 3.5mm 1/8" Headphone Extension Cord Cable. Up for bid is a 6 foot long, 3.5mm (1/8") stereo audio extension cable. It has a male 3.5mm mini plug (like the one you plug into portable CD players) on one end, and a female 3.5mm mini jack on the other end. This cable is perfect to be used as an extension for stereo headphones, speakers, microphones etc. 12 foot and 25 foot lengths cables are also available (please see my other listings). Stereo Audio Extension Cable. Suitable for General Audio Applications. 2.8mm OD Black PVC Jacket. 4.5mm OD Black PVC Guitar Cord Jacket. Fully Molded Construction. Nickel-plated connectors provide superior protection against corrosion. AWG26 Stranded Copper Center Conductor. Low-Loss 95% Spiral-Wound Copper Shield. 99.99% Pure Oxygen-Free Copper Wire. We also carry 12ft and 25ft lengths
